---
import { Sparkles, Hand, Target, BookOpen, HandHelping, Bot, FlaskConical, Rocket, User, Mail, Newspaper, FolderGit2, Library, Info } from 'lucide-astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于摩索 AI - 记录 AI Agent 开发的探索之路">
  <article class="about">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="logo-section">
        <img src="/logo.svg" alt="摩索 AI Logo" class="about-logo" />
        <h1>关于 摩索 AI</h1>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <Hand size={32} class="section-icon" />
      <h2>品牌寓意</h2>
      <p class="story-text">
        "摩索"二字，取自"揣摩技术，探索前沿"。我们希望成为 AI Agent 时代每一位开发者的同行者与索引者。
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <Hand size={32} class="section-icon" />
      <h2>这里是哪里？</h2>
      <p>
        摩索 AI 是一个记录 AI Agent 开发探索之路的地方。这里分享 OpenClaw、Hermes Agent
        等工具的实战经验、教程和心得。
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <Target size={32} class="section-icon" />
      <h2>为什么要做这个？</h2>
      <p>
        AI Agent 是个新领域，文档少、坑多。我在摸索过程中踩了不少坑，也积累了一些经验。
        把这些记录下来，希望能帮到同样在探索的人。
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <BookOpen size={32} class="section-icon" />
      <h2>内容方向</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <Newspaper size={32} class="card-icon" />
          <h3>资讯</h3>
          <p>AI Agent 领域最新动态和前沿资讯</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <FlaskConical size={32} class="card-icon" />
          <h3>评测</h3>
          <p>各种 AI 开发工具的深度评测和对比</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <BookOpen size={32} class="card-icon" />
          <h3>教程</h3>
          <p>OpenClaw、Hermes Agent 等工具的实战教程</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <FolderGit2 size={32} class="card-icon" />
          <h3>开源</h3>
          <p>开源项目分享和代码实战</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <Library size={32} class="card-icon" />
          <h3>资源</h3>
          <p>精选学习资源和工具推荐</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <Info size={32} class="card-icon" />
          <h3>关于</h3>
          <p>关于我们和联系方式</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <User size={32} class="section-icon" />
      <h2>关于作者</h2>
      <p>
        老李，一个在 AI Agent 领域摸索的开发者。有糖尿病，总是熬夜，做事有点拖拉，
        但认真起来会忘记时间。
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <Mail size={32} class="section-icon" />
      <h2>联系我</h2>
      <p>
        有问题或建议？欢迎交流。
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .logo-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-logo {
    height: 80px;
    width: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-accent) 100%);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .section-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .section p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .story-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md), 0 0 20px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.15);
  }

  .card-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
